snippet.title: Fairy Tail - PV2
snippet.description:
Your #FairyTail adventure in Fiore awaits you!
PS4/Switch: 7/31/20
PC: 7/30/20
                                                                                                                                                                 Get ready to build a five-character dream team from a roster of over 15 playable characters as they adventure across the Kingdom of Fiore in their quest to raise FAIRY TAIL to the top guild in the region.                                                                                                                                                           
                                                                                                                                                            Want to learn more about the game?
Visit our website: https://www.fairytailgame.com/us/
                                                                                                                                                           #FairyTail #FairyTailGame #HiroMashima
